{
  "stem": "3212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When she heard that-- her name was Greta-- she committed suicide with her child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She went in the kitchen, opened the gas, and killed herself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was another uncle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Months, maybe three, four months after my uncle-- the two uncles went to Poland, suddenly one of their sons and sisters, Walter Riegler and Anne Riegler, came back from Poland.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they reported to us that when they arrived everybody in Poland, they put all-- thousands of families in one little place, without food, without nothing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they started to-- these people had to start digging graves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they killed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my cousin and his sister ran away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they arrived in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told her that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were hiding in our place, in our apartment, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you feel about it as a child?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were you scared?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was scared-- the moment00 from the moment that Hitler came, I was already scared.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was really scared because I-- I lost all my friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the friends that I thought they're my friends, they start calling me dirty Jew, schwein, pig Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody wanted to talk to us anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only one that we had was our family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were afraid, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What I didn't mention before, my uncle, Max, that came with us to Vienna, too, and his aunt-- and my aunt and her son, they arrested him and sent him to Dachau, the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But in that time, in 1940, they started building this concentration camp, Dachau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after he was there five or six months, they told him that if he is leaving Austria in 24 hours with his family, they-- they release him from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That time, they didn't kill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the camps, they build it only.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
